A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Health Care Facilities – Rights of Comprehensive and Extended Care Facility
3 Residents – Hospice Comfort Care
4 FOR the purpose of providing for an exception to the prohibition on a comprehensive care
5 facility and an extended care facility using physical and chemical restraints on
6 certain residents for sedatives, anti–anxiety medication, bed rails, and geri chairs
7 authorized by a prescriber for patients receiving hospice care; and generally relating
8 to the rights of residents at comprehensive and extended care facilities.
