23 (a) In this section and §§ 19–344, 19–345, 19–345.1, 19–345.2, and 19–345.3 of
24 this subtitle, “facility” means a related institution that, under the rules and regulations of
25 the Department, is a comprehensive care facility or an extended care facility.
